meta.job_title: Full Stack Developer / Front End Developer

duties_responsibilities.duty: Develop applications for AWS environment with a strong understanding of AWS services.
Create and maintain user interfaces using React.js and JavaScript.
Integrate and orchestrate APIs to connect multiple applications.
Review application requirements and interface designs, identifying web-based user interactions.
Collaborate with the development team to discuss and implement user interface ideas and applications.
Write application interface codes using JavaScript following react.js workflows.
Troubleshoot and debug software applications as needed.
